{"tid":1477752,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解藍絲死都唔會割啊？唔係因為佢哋愛政府愛黨愛警察","createTime":"2019-08-16T08:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T07:16:04.000Z","uid":287856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d94fd45e23249a2a4806eb6392168c73149c80ac","tid":1477752,"uid":287856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:33:53.000Z","msg":"而係因為做藍絲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無後果唔會觸犯法律</span></span>啊！！<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">共產黨</span>勢力大，難倒台<br />\n佢哋深信有<span style=\"color: blue;\">共產黨</span>撐，講咩都係冇事<br />\n如果警察俾<span style=\"color: red;\">國際</span>定罪<br />\n如果政府俾<span style=\"color: red;\">國際</span>否定<br />\n佢哋仲敢唔敢公然大條道理咁講</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">818</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">緊記FOCUS翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">1. 徹底撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n3. 必不追究反送中抗爭者<br />\n4. 成立獨立委員會，徹查警方濫權濫暴、包括612暴力清場、721警黑合流、811血腥鎮壓<br />\n5. 全面落實雙真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Je4FF6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJe4FF6f.jpg&h=243549ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a5c02e489e9cbb3f9fbb0ec00ab405ba7a29f7d","tid":1477752,"uid":287856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"48e30a0b38ea05ac7bac516e957e5d03560ce9e0","tid":1477752,"uid":287856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:34:19.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"dc833007ccd533cadb374d644ba8b5cc6991e8ed","tid":1477752,"uid":287856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"11e6265c608dadd4848c09687b481e797ab09d52","tid":1477752,"uid":287856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"